# Notice

This project began as a Japanese-language adaptation of
epoko77-ai/im-not-ai, licensed under the MIT License.

The initial repository history, installation approach, plugin packaging,
and skill architecture were derived from the original project. The Japanese
detection taxonomy, rewriting rules, prompts, examples, and evaluation
materials are maintained independently here.

Legacy Korean upstream material is retained under legacy/upstream-korean/
for attribution and reference. It is not installed by the default scripts.
